My First Pet Project :) ... Extracting Download Links by Searching for emails from a 
particular person and then recursively going through the emails and extracting Attachment links. 
Then, give any Web Interface you want! :) .. (Mobile, Web, incorporate in any other project!!).. 
And yes, using Convertigo for extracting the attachment links (www.convertigo.com)


